    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rose has just moved to a small town ready to start a new life. Luckily, she quickly found a job as a receptionist at the Helios Hotel, the fancy new hotel in town. Her first day proves working at the Helios Hotel isn't quite what she was expecting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Rose and perform the functions of the hotel receptionist while uncovering strange occurrences that begin to unfold more and more each night. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045330/extras/Pumpkin_Guy_Small.PNG?t=1769279626\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a short indie horror game broken down into chapters. There are four chapters with the full game taking around 1 hour to complete. Each chapter may take an average of 15 minutes to complete depending on how much exploration is done.</p>",
